  "title": "Sales Engineer (Valves/ Pumps)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>In charge of generating new leads</li>\n  <li>Responsible in providing professional services to the existing and new clients through consultative selling, cross-selling or up-selling the company’s products and/or services.</li>\n  <li>In charge of establishing and maintaining strong and lasting relationships with clients by regularly updating them with company’s new products and introducing innovative solutions</li>\n  <li>In charge of providing continuing pre-sales and post-sales support in managing and meeting their expectations.</li>\n  <li>In charge of developing and customising relevant materials and presentations that explain key product features and viable technical solutions to benefit clients and prospects.</li>\n  <li>In charge of maintaining a high degree of technical knowledge to effectively engage in business discussions with clients across industries, and to co-create feasible solutions to address any of their engineering concerns throughout the selling process.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in managing accounts effectively throughout the sales cycle</li>\n  <li>In charge of preparing costing, tenders, proposals and quotations to current and new clients.</li>\n  <li>Provide weekly report updates of sales, pipelines, leads, opportunities and sales activities</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Diploma in Engineering</li>\n  <li>Min 3 years of working experience in doing sales in Refineries/Petrochemical Industry</li>\n  <li>Possess own transport will be advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br>\n<strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
